      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as an economical option for someone seeking a practical daily driver, starter car, or project opportunity. It presents honestly for its age and use, and it delivers a lot of utility at an accessible price point. A smart buy for anyone who wants dependable mobility without a major investment.",
