    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, budget-friendly runabout, or a handy spare car? This one has plenty of life left for the right buyer and offers a great chance to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune. It\u2019s the kind of car that could suit someone practical, mechanically minded, or anyone who sees the value in a straightforward deal. Priced to make sense and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
