      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget driver with good bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts up, runs, and moves out well, with a healthy powertrain feel and straightforward mechanical layout that makes it an ideal daily beater, backup car, or light project. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present throughout, but underneath it\u2019s a practical, no-nonsense vehicle with dependable transportation potential. If you want something affordable that still feels mechanically honest and worth putting miles on, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Used and rough, priced to sell fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence you notice before you even turn the key\u2014a seasoned machine with real personality and a story in every panel. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who appreciates charm over pretense: a budget-friendly ride, a hands-on project, or a dependable companion for the right owner with vision. There\u2019s an honest, lived-in feel here that makes it stand out from sterile, forgettable transport, and at this price, it opens the door to possibilities without asking for a huge commitment. If you\u2019ve been looking for something affordable with character and potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
